{"version":2,"title":"Left Hand of Darkness","author":"Ursula K. le Guin","state":{"lastAnalyzedIndex":21,"result":{"characters":[{"name":"Genly Ai","aliases":["Mr. Ai","the Envoy"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"1. A Parade in Erhenrang","currentLocation":"Erhenrang","description":"The Gethenian Envoy from the Ekumen, tasked with establishing contact with Karhide.","relationships":[{"character":"Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","relationship":"The Envoy, under Estraven's patronage"},{"character":"King Argaven XV","relationship":"Target of Ai's diplomatic mission"}],"recentEvents":"Engaged in tense dialogue with Estraven about political tensions and the Ekumen's role."},{"name":"Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","aliases":["The King’s Ear","Lord Estraven"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"1. A Parade in Erhenrang","currentLocation":"Royal House","description":"Karhide's prime minister, politically astute but conflicted about his loyalty.","relationships":[{"character":"King Argaven XV","relationship":"Prime minister and political advisor"},{"character":"Genly Ai","relationship":"Distrustful contact with ambiguous motives"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed border disputes, patriotism, and the Ekumen with Ai, revealing his political disillusionment."},{"name":"King Argaven XV","aliases":["the king"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"1. A Parade in Erhenrang","currentLocation":"Royal House","description":"The ruler of Karhide, overseeing the completion of the River Gate Arch.","relationships":[{"character":"Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","relationship":"Prime minister and advisor"},{"character":"Genly Ai","relationship":"Subject and target of diplomatic efforts"}],"recentEvents":"Refused to engage with Ai's mission, perceiving it as a threat to his authority."},{"name":"Pemmer Harge rem ir Tibe","aliases":["the king’s cousin"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"1. A Parade in Erhenrang","currentLocation":"Unknown","